<mvc:View controllerName="deloitte.r2022.controller.Home" 
	xmlns="sap.m" 
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
	xmlns:semantic="sap.m.semantic">
	<Page title="{i18n>appTitle}" class="sapUiContentPadding" showNavButton="false">
		<content>
			<GenericTile class="sapUiTinyMarginBegin sapUiTinyMarginTop tileLayout" header="{i18n>homeViewTile1}" subheader="" press="onNavTile1">
				<TileContent unit="" footer="">
					<ImageContent class='dl-tile-icon' src="sap-icon://laptop" />
				</TileContent>
			</GenericTile>
			<GenericTile class="sapUiTinyMarginBegin sapUiTinyMarginTop tileLayout" header="{i18n>homeViewTile2}" subheader="" press="onPress">
				<TileContent unit="" footer="">
					<ImageContent class='dl-tile-icon' src="sap-icon://dimension" />
				</TileContent>
			</GenericTile>
			<GenericTile class="sapUiTinyMarginBegin sapUiTinyMarginTop tileLayout" header="{i18n>homeViewTile3}" subheader="" press="onPress">
				<TileContent unit="" footer="">
					<ImageContent class='dl-tile-icon' src="sap-icon://edit" />
				</TileContent>
			</GenericTile>
		</content>
		<footer>
			<Toolbar>
				<ToolbarSpacer/>
				<Button text="Accept" type="Accept" />
				<Button text="Reject" type="Reject" />
				<Button text="Edit" />
				<Button text="Delete" />
			</Toolbar>
		</footer>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>